Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.37,0:01:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,THE CLASH OF POWERFUL SWORDS
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.00,0:01:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My sword realizes it!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.30,0:02:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Don't use your crest at full power!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.59,0:02:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to conserve your energy!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.68,0:02:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,No! He's not the Hadorra we knew!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.47,0:02:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to fight\Nwith my full strength or we'll die!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.31,0:02:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,An astute observation!\NYou truly are my rival!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.34,0:02:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I expect nothing less\Nfrom a Disciple of Aban!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.31,0:02:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.70,0:03:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hadorra's completely changed!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.25,0:03:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a complete monster now!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.96,0:03:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I've seen those features somewhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.19,0:03:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,C-Could he be a Superior Being?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.82,0:03:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.70,0:03:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He was converted\Nusing the data Zamuza sent!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.95,0:03:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right, Hadorra?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.41,0:03:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll see when you fight me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.08,0:03:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You can experience it yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.75,0:04:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,This power I obtained\Nby sacrificing everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.77,0:04:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And realize...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.35,0:04:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,compared to all the powerful enemies\Nthat you've fought...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.77,0:04:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,just how powerful I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.71,0:04:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.22,0:04:49.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Th-That's impossible!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.81,0:04:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I blocked him with\Nthe crest power focused in my right hand!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.60,0:04:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's numb!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.73,0:04:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't draw my sword like this!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.91,0:05:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}IORA!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.92,0:05:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,A-A spell?! How?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.97,0:05:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought Superior Beings\Ncouldn't cast spells!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.48,0:05:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop, Hadorra!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.10,0:05:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.23,0:05:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it. We're at a ceasefire for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.49,0:05:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Out of respect for Commander Hadorra.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.24,0:05:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, this is a one-on-one duel\Nbetween him and Dai.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.95,0:06:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Get real! We never agreed\Nto any one-on-one business!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.63,0:06:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe you have an obligation\Nto see this duel through.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.88,0:06:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Hadorra can no longer become a Darkling.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.26,0:06:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,He gave up everything for this battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.10,0:06:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Gave up?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.31,0:06:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.98,0:06:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,In order to be able to cast spells,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.56,0:06:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,he gave up the ability to turn from\Na Superior Being back to a Darkling!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.24,0:06:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,So Hadorra is stuck\Nin that monster form forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.78,0:06:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.29,0:06:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate to admit it, but as a result\Nhe has gotten just a little stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.42,0:06:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup, yup!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.17,0:06:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Just a little"?! Are you kidding me?!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.71,0:06:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A Superior Being that can cast spells?!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.30,0:06:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's a formula for true flawlessness!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.72,0:07:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I no longer care for my Darkling body!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.73,0:07:03.73,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, by giving it up,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.90,0:07:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I was able to discard my foolish pride as\Nthe Dark Lord who dominated the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.03,0:07:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,True victory can never be attained\Nby one obsessed with reputation!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.83,0:07:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a lesson\Nyour master Aban taught me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.55,0:07:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's strong!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.76,0:07:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Not only that,\Nhe's more resolute than ever before!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.01,0:07:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't beat him without my sword!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.89,0:07:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I need to draw it\Nwith my left hand somehow!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.88,0:08:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}IORA!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.26,0:08:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Wave Slash!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.73,0:08:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.28,0:08:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's your new sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.24,0:08:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well.\NWe shall see with your next strike,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.54,0:08:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,whether the power within my right arm
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.46,0:08:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,is stronger than the power of your sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.26,0:08:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The power within his right arm?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.72,0:08:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Does he have a power\Ngreater than those claws?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.85,0:09:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.68,0:09:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I've seen the awesome destructive power\Nof the Sword of Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.69,0:09:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what sort of\Nkiller attack he has,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.57,0:09:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,it can't be stronger than that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.16,0:09:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai, hurry up and finish it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.62,0:09:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't forget that Superior Beings\Nregenerate while fighting!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.08,0:09:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I know that, Popp.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.75,0:09:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I intend to finish it!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.42,0:09:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Good. The feeling's returned!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.68,0:09:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.68,0:09:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Dragonic Aura!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.40,0:09:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.48,0:09:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.86,0:10:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Aban Strash.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.37,0:10:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The attack that cleaved Sovereign\NRock Castle was probably Earth Slash.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.70,0:10:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And he just used Wave Slash.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.67,0:10:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,This will be the first Aban Strash\Nthe Sword of Dai unleashes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.96,0:10:18.47,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what\Namazing power you have hidden,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.63,0:10:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,it can't beat this strike\NI've filled with all my power!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.76,0:10:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Then try it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.10,0:10:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're right, I'll be cleaved in two.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.94,0:10:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,But I will be testing myself, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.48,0:10:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The ultimate being\Nsaid to be of divine creation...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.28,0:10:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,A strike from such a Dragon Knight...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.04,0:10:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,will reveal just how complete a weapon\NI, Hadorra the Superior Being, have become!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.88,0:10:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,He seems pretty confident.\NI wonder what power he's gained.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.34,0:11:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I won't lose!\NNot while I have the Sword of Dai!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.55,0:11:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No matter who I face!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.48,0:11:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I won't lose!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.19,0:11:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Here goes, Hadorra!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.77,0:11:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.36,0:11:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\\i1}{\\3c&H1717E4&}Aban...{\\i0}{\\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.86,0:11:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\\i1}{\\3c&H1717E4&}Strash!{\\i0}{\\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.95,0:11:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Did it work?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.47,0:11:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,That's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.06,0:11:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,A direct hit from the Sword of Dai,\Nand his arm isn't even cut!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.89,0:11:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Is his... Is Hadorra's body\Nharder than Orichalcum?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.03,0:12:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-That's not it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.74,0:12:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I felt the impact of something metallic!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.99,0:12:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right, Dai. I have one, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.46,0:12:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,A legendary weapon equal to your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.84,0:12:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The Sword of Champions.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.55,0:12:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,The Sword of Champions?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.80,0:12:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right! Zamuza gave it to Hadorra!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.39,0:12:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed. The real Sword of Champions...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.48,0:12:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,is right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.65,0:12:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,In my right arm!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.00,0:12:54.58,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}ABAN STRASH{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.00,0:12:59.59,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,REAPER FLUTE
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.80,0:13:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yow!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.97,0:13:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Could this Dark Aura be...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.68,0:13:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Dark Fire Energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.10,0:13:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.89,0:13:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Dark Fire Energy! Dark! Fire! Energy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.69,0:13:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,A Dark Aura that burns life energy\Nbeyond its limits!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.45,0:13:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.95,0:13:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I can tell from that strike!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.37,0:13:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,My power is on par with\Nthat of a Dragon Knight!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.29,0:13:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And with an equal weapon,\Nmy fighting power is greater!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.22,0:13:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.31,0:13:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,But I won't hold back!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.56,0:14:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,To not fight with my fullest abilities\Nwould be disrespectful!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.32,0:14:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Take this, Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.98,0:14:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,A strike I unleash\Nusing the Sword of Champions!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.25,0:14:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\\i1}{\\3c&H1717E4&}Ultra Combustion Slash!{\\i0}{\\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.00,0:14:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Ultra Combustion Slash?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.55,0:14:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Not a bad idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.92,0:14:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,By using Dark Fire Energy\Nalong his sword,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.43,0:14:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,the power of his attack is magnified.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.93,0:14:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.39,0:14:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai! Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.64,0:14:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get hit!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.35,0:14:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I-I can't! It's too late!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.44,0:14:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I have to defend with my Dragonic Aura!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.49,0:14:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My Aura's weak!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.08,0:14:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.04,0:15:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my. Did he finish him?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.59,0:15:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Look there!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.14,0:15:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,A Rura spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.31,0:15:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp jumped in and rescued Dai.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.94,0:15:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It's supposed to be one-on-one!\NYou cheater!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.94,0:15:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! They're running! Get back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.95,0:15:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,They won't get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.55,0:15:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh wow! He's super fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.26,0:15:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's follow them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.72,0:16:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I never thought\NI'd be called a cheater by them!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.27,0:16:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,P-Popp... Why...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.98,0:16:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai, I'll be honest with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.90,0:16:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't beat Hadorra alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.16,0:16:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Until now, he always tended\Nto give in to his emotions.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.25,0:16:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's why even I was able\Nto match him somehow.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.79,0:16:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,But Hadorra's changed!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.38,0:16:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,He isn't just stronger\Nfrom becoming a Superior Being!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.68,0:16:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like his mind has been cleared!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.34,0:16:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Guys like that\Nwho don't waver are dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.77,0:16:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd know. I've been there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.18,0:16:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,B-But...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.64,0:16:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough! We're going back to Papunica!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.27,0:16:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,We're already exhausted\Nfrom fighting Sovereign Rock Castle!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.32,0:16:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.24,0:16:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Rura!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.99,0:17:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh crap! I've used too much Magic Power!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.33,0:17:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Popp?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.83,0:17:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry! Let's just run\Nas far as possible with Toberura!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.26,0:17:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you going, Popp?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.01,0:17:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You're headed East.\NThat's not the way back.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.92,0:18:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you like\Nmy flawless Superior Being?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.43,0:18:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,If he defeats Dai, it will mean\Nhe's surpassed a Dragon Knight!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.77,0:18:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,He will be greater than\Nthe god-created Dragon Knight!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.06,0:18:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Meaning I've surpassed the gods!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.07,0:18:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Surely it's safe to say now\Nthat I am a god!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.03,0:18:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He can already use Toberura\Nwithout the use of his crest.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.96,0:18:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't take my eyes off him for a second.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.09,0:18:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai! Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.18,0:18:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.06,0:18:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Popp, run! While I'm keeping him busy!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.98,0:18:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,The power of your crest has faded.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.48,0:18:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That means your Dragonic Aura is gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.20,0:19:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like I win!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.45,0:19:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I have to attack!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.87,0:19:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Defending with what Dragonic Aura or\NMagic Power I have left won't be enough!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.13,0:19:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's over! Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.46,0:19:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Anything! Some sort of attack that uses\Nall my Aura and Magic Power at once!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.22,0:19:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\\i1}{\\3c&H1717E4&}Ultra Combustion Slash!{\\i0}{\\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.90,0:19:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,L-Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.24,0:19:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.45,0:19:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.75,0:19:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,He got Dai?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.04,0:19:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.46,0:19:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.67,0:19:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.01,0:20:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.09,0:20:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.31,0:20:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.23,0:20:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-This can't be happening!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.61,0:20:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The Sword of Dai\Nwas supposed to be unrivaled!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.66,0:20:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Come out, Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.57,0:20:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Get back here and fight back!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.95,0:20:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,H-He defeated the Hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.00,0:20:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,A clash between Orichalcum weapons\Nmeans conditions are matched.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.46,0:20:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,In terms of physical strength,\Na Superior Being is more powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.76,0:20:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,This is probably Hadorra's victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.43,0:20:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no fair. He's hogging all the glory.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.81,0:21:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Hadorra!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.48,0:21:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,See? Hadorra wins.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.55,0:21:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,A true Hero.\NI'd be disappointed otherwise.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.31,0:21:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hadorra, too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.40,0:21:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I-It was a draw?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.70,0:21:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Myst, go see to Hadorra, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.66,0:21:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.37,0:21:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,will take care of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.46,0:22:07.43,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tatoe akuma ni seiron kazashite\Nmukatte mitemo{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.46,0:22:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if you face the devil\NWith logic on your side{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.59,0:22:11.39,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}sore wa akumade seitouka\Nsashite chigai wa naikamo{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.59,0:22:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It may just be a rationalization{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.55,0:22:15.47,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}ima mo ima mo yureteiru kedo{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.55,0:22:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even now, even now I waver{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.64,0:22:19.52,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}bokura wa dokomade yukuno{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.64,0:22:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How far will we go?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.69,0:22:22.82,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tenshi no sasayaki nimo nita\Nkoe ga kikoeta{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.69,0:22:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I heard a voice like an angel's whisper{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.98,0:22:26.74,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}hatamata petenshi no mayakashi\Nhitokiwa mimi ni hibiiteita{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.98,0:22:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Maybe it was an imposter's illusion\NIt still rang in my ears{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.90,0:22:30.45,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}ai ni hiai ni sarasare nagara{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.90,0:22:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Exposed to love and sorrow{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.61,0:22:34.74,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}hokori mamire michi no tochu{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.61,0:22:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}On the path strewn with pride{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.45,0:22:38.79,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}kiete wa ukabu touhikou{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.45,0:22:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Fleeting moments of cowardice{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.33,0:22:42.59,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}nomikonda SOS{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.33,0:22:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The SOS I held back{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.17,0:22:48.17,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}furueru te wo nigirishimeta{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.17,0:22:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I clenched my trembling fist{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.76,0:22:53.76,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tatta hitotsu no chiisana yakusoku ga{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.76,0:22:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That single little promise{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.93,0:22:57.56,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}honno sasaina omoidetachi ga{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.93,0:22:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Those trivial little memories{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.73,0:22:59.85,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}itsumade tattemo kono mune wo{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.73,0:22:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They're still in my heart{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.02,0:23:04.02,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}kogashi tsuzukeru tomoshibi ni naru{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.02,0:23:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As embers that keep me burning{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.19,0:23:08.53,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tada hitosuji no toumei na hikari ga{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.19,0:23:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A single transparent beam of light{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.69,0:23:11.70,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}me no mae wo terashite yuku{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.69,0:23:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Lights the way before me{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.86,0:23:16.41,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}boku ni dekiru koto wa ikutsu mo naisa{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.86,0:23:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There is little that I can do{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.54,0:23:22.58,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}shinjinuita saki ni te ni shita mirai wo\Nsusunde yuke{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.54,0:23:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just keep on to the future\NI managed to grasp through my faith{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.30,0:23:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dai and Hadorra's fierce battle\Nhas ended in a draw.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.52,0:23:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wounded, Hadorra leaves the battlefield.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.85,0:23:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Meanwhile, Dai remains missing\Nafter falling into the ocean.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.65,0:23:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Left alone, Popp is hounded by Kilban.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.28,0:23:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Can Popp manage to survive?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.32,0:23:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And what happened to Dai?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.99,0:23:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,DRAGON QUEST The Adventure of Dai{\i1},{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.45,0:23:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"The Hero Lost in the Glacier"{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.24,0:24:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The adventure continues!{\i}
